import React from 'react';
import { Paper, Typography, Box, Accordion, AccordionSummary, AccordionDetails, Grid } from '@mui/material';
import { ExpandMore } from '@mui/icons-material';

const TrainingHistory = ({ history }) => {
  return (
    <Paper sx={{ p: 2, maxHeight: '80vh', overflow: 'auto' }}>
      <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
        Training History
      </Typography>
      {history.map((entry, index) => (
        <Accordion key={entry.timestamp}>
          <AccordionSummary expandIcon={<ExpandMore />}>
            <Typography>
              Model #{history.length - index} - {new Date(entry.timestamp).toLocaleString()}
            </Typography>
          </AccordionSummary>
          <AccordionDetails>
            <Box>
              <Typography variant="subtitle2" gutterBottom>
                Architecture:
              </Typography>
              {entry.architecture.map((layer, layerIndex) => (
                <Box key={layerIndex} sx={{ ml: 2, mb: 1 }}>
                  <Grid container spacing={1}>
                    <Grid item xs={12}>
                      <Typography variant="body2">
                        {layer.type}:
                      </Typography>
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs={12}>
                      <Box sx={{ pl: 2 }}>
                        {Object.entries(layer.params).map(([key, value]) => (
                          <Typography key={key} variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                            {key}: {value}
                          </Typography>
                        ))}
                      </Box>
                    </Grid>
                  </Grid>
                </Box>
              ))}
              <Typography variant="subtitle2" gutterBottom sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
                Training Config:
              </Typography>
              <Box sx={{ ml: 2 }}>
                <Typography variant="body2">Optimizer: {entry.optimizer}</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2">Learning Rate: {entry.learning_rate}</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2">Epochs: {entry.epochs}</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2">Total Parameters: {entry.total_params.toLocaleString()}</Typography>
              </Box>
              <Typography variant="subtitle2" gutterBottom sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
                Results:
              </Typography>
              <Box sx={{ ml: 2 }}>
                <Typography variant="body2">
                  Final Training Accuracy: {(entry.final_train_accuracy * 100).toFixed(2)}%
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2">
                  Final Test Accuracy: {(entry.final_test_accuracy * 100).toFixed(2)}%
                </Typography>
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </AccordionDetails>
        </Accordion>
      ))}
      {history.length === 0 && (
        <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" textAlign="center" py={4}>
          No training history yet
        </Typography>
      )}
    </Paper>
  );
};

export default TrainingHistory;
